
Thief help - Steal
==================
command: steal <item> from <creature>

Thieves can steal what others would needlessly labor to obtain.
Thieves know the value of a good days work, or lack thereof.
The sly shall prevail where the strong of arm will fail.
Legend level thieves may even find that they can slip worn objects
away from the unsuspecting owner.

Stats: Dex
==================

